column4:
Ugh――
if I wait too long, I'll get even hungrier, 
so please, as soon as you can.

My buddy's fighting on the pier up ahead, 
he's a little wounded, not moving too well; 
give me a hand--!

As for the collapsed well, 
if it could be restored to how it was before, 
I'd have no further complaints.

I told Lorna I might not be back
for a week and left the dining hall to her,
so everything's covered!
